data.description: Tucked away in the serene embrace of a cul-de-sac in Rancho Escondido! Discover this energy-efficient home that harmoniously blends charm & comfort. Inside, you're instantly captivated by the bright living & dining room featuring tile flooring in the main areas & soaring ceilings exuding a sense of grandeur and openness. Desirable great room has back patio access, ensuring seamless indoor-outdoor living. The kitchen comes w/track lighting, honey oak cabinetry, a pantry, SS appliances, solid surface counters, & a breakfast nook. Sizable loft is excellent for a reading nook/office. Carpeted primary bedroom has a window seat, an ensuite w/dual sinks, & a walk-in closet. You'll find a haven of relaxation in the spacious backyard, providing a covered patio, pavers, and a fire pit. Act now.
